word_mean_info__list.difference: 指规模较小，出售同一类商品的店铺。
在美国指出售同一类商品的小型商店。在英国用复数形式表示百货商店。
作商店解时，是美国英语，通常写为department store。
较正式用词，指小心地使用难以补充的资源或贵重物，免遭浪费或毁坏，以备不时之需。
普通用词，指将物品存放，以备将来使用。
普通用词，指尽量少用，以争取数量上有所增加。
侧重将物品完好无损地保存下来。

bilingual.target: 今天就去你当地的商店看看。

bilingual.source: There is nothing new in the store.
bilingual.target: 商店里没有什么新东西。

bilingual.source: Someone took the video back to the store.
bilingual.target: 有人把录像带拿回了商店。

bilingual.source: You can buy clothes and furniture in a department store.
bilingual.target: 你可以在百货商店买衣服和家具。

bilingual.source: You can find anything you want in that department store.
bilingual.target: 你可以在那个百货商店找到任何你想要的东西。

bilingual.source: Despite not having any money, Laith spent hours in the department store.
bilingual.target: 尽管没有钱，莱斯在百货商店里待了好几个小时。

bilingual.source: You go to the store to buy another pair of earrings that looks similar to the missing pair.
bilingual.target: 你去商店买另一对看起来和丢失的耳环相似的耳环。

list.abstract: 《Store》是Carly Rae Jepsen（卡莉·蕾·吉普森）演唱的一首歌曲，收录在专辑《Emotion Side B》中，于2016年8月26日正式发行。

yingyinNormal.en: Where is Elizabeth? She's at the store. You make the girl go to the store? Do I know where the store is?
yingyinNormal.zh: 伊丽莎白呢？她去买东西。你让女生去买东西？我知道商店在哪里吗？

yingyinNormal.en: What are you going to get at the train store, Sheldon?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你打算去商店里买点什么呢，谢尔顿？

yingyinNormal.en: Get your face painted here. Suzy Sheep is in charge of the panting face store.
yingyinNormal.zh: 来这画脸啦。苏西负责画脸商店。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm just gonna run to the store and get a few things. I'll pick you up when you're done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我去商店里买点东西，等你剪完再来接你。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't have iced tea and snickerdoodles. A good wife would go to the store.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我家没有冻柠茶和曲奇饼。尽职的妻子就会去商店买。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry, as I was saying the store number is wrong, and I'm sorry but that's... Oh my God.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对不起，我刚才说商店号码是错的。对不起，可是…我的天。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know where the store is? No. Do you wanna ride around town on my little pink bicycle? A little bit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道商店在哪里吗？不知道。你想骑粉红脚踏车逛大街吗？有点想。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know what's in this but it is not paprika. I'm gonna go to the store, I'll be back in 20 minutes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道这是什么，但肯定不是辣椒粉。我去趟商店，20分钟就回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Nobody Beats the Wiz, the electronics store. Stock boy. What do you think? You're not gonna work at that place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无敌天才电器商店，仓储员 你觉得怎么样？你不能去那种地方工作。

yingyinNormal.en: The average store has over 45,000 products on its shelves, and roughly a third of them are created using corn.
yingyinNormal.zh: 平均每家商店货架上有45000种产品，这其中几乎三分之一来自于玉米。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm going to the store later. In the meantime, you can have some fruit. That's real? I thought it was just for show.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我晚点会去商店。这之前你可以吃点水果。那是真的吗？我还以为只是装饰品。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, that's right. You're the talker. Anyway, great idea. I gotta go to the store. I told him that I would buy him some more tissues.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，话多的是你，总之这个主意很棒，我要去商店，我答应去帮他买面纸。

yingyinNormal.en: What's to know? Buy sell, high low, bears bulls. Yes Manhattan. Yeah telephone number of the stock, selling store.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要通什么？买，卖，高，低，熊市，牛市。喂，曼哈顿麻烦帮我查个电话号码，股票商店。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, well, well, Sheldon, fancy meeting you here. I guess the train store in Glendale wasn't having a cotillion after all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧瞧，谢尔顿，真没想到会碰到你啊，我猜格兰岱尔市的火车玩具商店根本就没举办沙龙舞会。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, getting to the ceremony on time. Leonard, quick. I need you to get me to Arcadia within the hour. The train store's having a sale.
yingyinNormal.zh: 接下来，准时到达典礼。莱纳德，快点。你得在一个小时内把我送到亚凯迪亚。火车模型商店正在大打折。

yingyinNormal.en: They stole Rowby's actual track. Then they recorded their own before putting it in the domestic iTunes store. That is theft. Actual theft.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们偷了罗比的原声带，然后才录了自己的版本，再放上国内的iTunes商店，那就是偷窃，十足的偷窃。

yingyinNormal.en: Why can't Amy drive you? Because of the tradition that I cannot see Amy on the day of the train store sale. Please, please see a doctor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 艾米为什么不送你去？因为按传统来说在火车模型商店打折那天我不能和艾米碰面[应是婚礼前]。拜托你，去看看医生好不好。

yingyinNormal.en: Emily elephant is in charge of breakup store. Roll up, roll up. All sold for a bit of bucks. What a lot of brackens, Emily. Buck You will be busy all day selling it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大象艾米丽负责商店。瞧一瞧，看一看，只要很少的钱就能买到。好多凤尾草啊，艾米丽。你今天一整天都要忙着卖这些东西了。

yingyinNormal.en: Over generations, they have built a self-sustaining village fashioned entirely out of bamboo and wood with its own post office, police station, convenient store, restaurants and medical center.
yingyinNormal.zh: 几世几代，他们建成了一座自给自足的村庄，全部由竹子和木材构建而成。有着自己的邮局、警察局、便利商店、饭店和医疗中心。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? In a comic book store?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在漫画店里这样好吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: On their own, taking our own bags to the grocery <highlight>store</highlight> or quitting plastic straws, for example, will accomplish little and require very little of us.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 比如，自己带购物袋去杂货店，或者停止使用塑料吸管，这样做的效果和要求都很低。

examination_example.sentence: Big chains have been collecting sales tax nationwide because they typically have physical <highlight>stores</highlight> in whatever state a purchase is being shipped to.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大型连锁企业一直在全国范围内征收销售税，因为它们通常在货物运输到的任何州都有实体店。

examination_example.sentence: In the late 1800s British archaeologist Sir Arthur Evans combed antique dealers' <highlight>stores</highlight> in Athens, Greece.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 19世纪末，英国考古学家Arthur Evans将希腊雅典的古董店仔细搜索了一遍。

examination_example.sentence: Phones are used to <highlight>store</highlight> sensitive information.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 手机被用来储存敏感信息。

examination_example.sentence: My mind seems to be able to cope and the information is <highlight>stored</highlight> away neatly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我的大脑似乎能够应付，信息也被整齐地储存起来。

examination_example.sentence: We often hear media reports that an unauthorized hacker has been able to access a computer database and to alter information <highlight>stored</highlight> there.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们经常听到媒体报道说，未经授权的黑客能够访问计算机数据库，并更改存储在那里的信息。

examination_example.sentence: Only recently have they come to see the vital part forests will have to play in <highlight>storing</highlight> carbon.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 直到最近，人们才开始意识到森林储碳的重要作用。

sense_info_list.en: goods of a particular kind or for a particular purpose

examination_example.sentence: Here was the raw material of houses and furniture, ships and potash, dyes and naval <highlight>stores</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这里有盖房、做家具、造船和生产钾碱、染料和松脂制品的原材料。

examination_example.sentence: Another clothing company, Patagonia, a high-end outdoor clothing <highlight>store</highlight>, follows the same principle.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 高端户外服装品牌巴塔哥尼亚 (Patagonia) 也有着同样的理念。

examination_example.sentence: Customers can bring shoes of any brand into an Adidas <highlight>store</highlight> to be shredded and turned into alternative fuels for energy creation.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消费者可以把任何品牌的废旧鞋子带到阿迪达斯商店，经过粉碎处理后转化为创造能源的可替代燃料。

examination_example.sentence: Power tool maker DeWalt partners with companies, such as Lowes and Napa Auto Parts, to collect old tools at their <highlight>stores</highlight> for recycling.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电动工具制造商得伟 (DeWalt) 与劳氏 (Lowes) 和纳帕汽车零部件 (Napa Auto Parts) 等公司合作，在商店回收旧工具。

examination_example.sentence: When customers do want to toss their pair, they can give them back to the <highlight>store</highlight>, which will repurpose and resell them.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果确实不再使用，消费者可以将不要的衣物送还商店，商店会重新加工，再次售卖。

examination_example.sentence: None of the chain's <highlight>stores</highlight> in the Washington metropolitan area are to be closed.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 华盛顿大都会地区的连锁店均不关闭。

examination_example.sentence: It will slash staffing at its fleet of 770 <highlight>stores</highlight>, a move affecting some 3, 000 employees.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该公司将在其770个舰队进行裁员，此举将影响约3000名员工。

examination_example.sentence: The retailer also announced the locations of 36 <highlight>stores</highlight> it will close in early 2016.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该零售商还宣布了将于2016年初关闭的36家商店的位置。

examination_example.sentence: Independence came in tying, wrapping, <highlight>storing</highlight>, harmonizing, and rationalizing that wardrobe.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 独立感体现在衣橱的打结、包装、存放、协调和合理化。

examination_example.sentence: Instead, some in Africa and Asia are seeing their first light bulbs illuminated by the power of sunlight <highlight>stored</highlight> in batteries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 相反，一些非洲和亚洲人见证了他们的第一个电灯泡是由存储在电池中的太阳能点亮的。

word_usage.usage: store用于复数时，可指“某类商品/物品”和“仓库”，也可指“（英国的）百货商店”。

examination_example.sentence: During the week, however, she likes to go to a nearby <highlight>store</highlight> to buy some small things she needs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，在一周中，她喜欢去附近的商店买一些她需要的小东西。

examination_example.sentence: Last week she walked up to the <highlight>store</highlight>, but when she went to pay for her groceries, she was short about three dollars.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 上周，她走到商店，但当她去支付食品杂货时，她缺了大约三美元。

examination_example.sentence: At this <highlight>store</highlight>, people check out and then go off to the side to bag their own groceries.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在这家商店里，人们退房，然后走到一边去打包他们自己的食品。

examination_example.sentence: Most of it is <highlight>stored</highlight> away or used for research.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大部分储存起来或用于研究。

examination_example.sentence: Lockers are available to <highlight>store</highlight> any belongings during your visit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 储物柜可用于存放您来访期间的任何物品。

examination_example.sentence: Many of the images were <highlight>stored</highlight> in an ice chest, under freezing water, in the damaged wooden ship.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多照片被保存在冰水中一艘破损木船的冰柜里。

examination_example.sentence: I was soon in the little general <highlight>store</highlight> that served our farming community.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我很快就来到了为我们农业社区服务的杂货店。

examination_example.sentence: After a while, my son came out of the <highlight>store</highlight>, and a new coat was in his hand.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 过了一会儿，我儿子从店里出来，手里拿着一件新外套。

examination_example.sentence: In a new civilization rich in machine intelligence, we have easy access to smart memory networks where information is <highlight>stored</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在一个充满机器智能的新文明中，我们可以很容易地访问存储信息的智能存储网络。

examination_example.sentence: Hospitals and blood banks <highlight>store</highlight> the blood and try to keep enough on hand.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 医院和血库储存血液，并尽量保持足够的库存。

examination_example.sentence: Many northern Chinese have the habit of <highlight>storing</highlight> food, especially for the long winter.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多北方中国人有储存食物的习惯，尤其是在漫长的冬天。

word_usage.usage: store用于复数时，可指“某类商品/物品”和“仓库”，也可指“（英国的）百货商店”。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 美国英语中的普通用词，指一般的商店，规模可大可小；在英国英语中可指出售各类物品的大商店，如大型超市或百货商店。
英国英语中的普通用词，一般指零售商店，在美国英语中则指出售某一种商品的小商店。
普通用词，指尽量少用，以争取数量上有所增加。
普通用词，指将物品存放，以备将来使用。
